OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCost of living: We cannot  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frule out a windfall tax,   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fsays minister              
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government "cannot rule out a      
OL,6, windfall tax" on oil and gas companies 
OL,7, to help with the rising cost of living,
OL,8, a Treasury minister has said.          
OL,10,FThe policy, proposed by opposition     
OL,11,Fparties, would see a one-off levy      
OL,12,Fimposed on the firms' profits, with    
OL,13,Fproceeds put towards help for hard hit 
OL,14,Fhouseholds facing surging bills.       
OL,16,FSimon Clarke said it was not a move he 
OL,17,Fwas "philosophically attracted" to.    
OL,19,FBut he said the government would       
OL,20,F"always act in a pragmatic fashion".   
